methods.name: InstructionStartOf
methods.logic: Returns the starting address of the instruction code for a given builtin.

methods.name: InstructionEndOf
methods.logic: Returns the ending address of the instruction code for a given builtin.

methods.name: InstructionSizeOf
methods.logic: Returns the size of the instruction code for a given builtin.

methods.name: MetadataStartOf
methods.logic: Returns the starting address of the metadata for a given builtin.

methods.name: InstructionStartOfBytecodeHandlers
methods.logic: Returns the starting address of the instruction code for the first bytecode handler.

methods.name: InstructionEndOfBytecodeHandlers
methods.logic: Returns the ending address of the instruction code for the bytecode handlers, including padding.

methods.name: PaddedInstructionSizeOf
methods.logic: Returns the padded and aligned size of the instruction code for a given builtin.
